# Design System

## Tailwind Color Tokens

theme: {
extend: {
colors: {
'saan-bone': '#FBF9F6',
'saan-maroon': '#3B0B14',
'saan-charcoal': '#121212',
'saan-gold': '#D4AF37',
'saan-champagne': '#EBE3D5',
'saan-ink': '#1C1A17',
}
}
}

## Color Usage

saan-bone:
Primary page background

saan-maroon:
Primary brand color

saan-charcoal:
Immersive dark sections

saan-gold:
Luxury accents only

saan-champagne:
Borders and dividers

saan-ink:
Primary text

## Borders

Use:

border-[0.5px]

Prefer:

- Hairline dividers
- Subtle separators

Avoid:

- Heavy borders
- Thick outlines

## Shadows

Use extremely subtle shadows.

Avoid:

- Material UI style shadows
- Floating cards
